<p class="contextTtl" id="p1" data-pid="1"><span id="page9" class="pageNum" aria-hidden="true" data-no="9" data-before-text="9"></span><strong>レッスン02</strong></p>
<h1 id="p2" data-pid="2"><strong>聖書を読むと希望が持てる</strong></h1>
</header>	<div class="clearfix alternatePresentation clickable noTooltips
		">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/41" class="lightbox"
